 as high as 0.125. We find that\n$U$=117.9$\\pm$1.8, which is in agreement with previous determinations. Using\nthe value $R_1=6.8 R_\\odot$ derived by Palate et al. (2013) the value of the\nobservational internal structure constant $k_{2,obs}$ is consistent with\ntheory. We confirm the presence of variability in the line profiles of the\nsecondary star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2016 16:13:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-06"}
