er-preserving squares and nontrivial parameterized cubes\n(nontrivial parameterized squares cannot be avoided in an infinite word).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2016 06:46:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-11"}
